<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Thanks for your purchase — Snipdrop Pro</title>
<meta name="robots" content="noindex">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,400;9..144,500;9..144,600&family=Inter:wght@400;450;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --ink:#13211d;--ink-soft:#33473f;--paper:#F2F7F4;--cream:#ffffff;--line:#d9e6df;
  --teal:#1D9E75;--teal-deep:#0f6e56;--teal-soft:#e3f4ed;--gold:#B8860B;--muted:#6f7d77;
  --shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(19,33,29,.04),0 8px 30px rgba(19,33,29,.07);
}
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{
  font-family:'Inter',-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
  background:var(--paper);color:var(--ink);line-height:1.6;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:32px 24px;
}
.display{font-family:'Fraunces',Georgia,serif;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.1}
a{color:inherit}
.card{
  background:var(--cream);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:22px;
  max-width:520px;width:100%;padding:44px 40px;text-align:center;box-shadow:var(--shadow);
}
.badge{
  width:72px;height:72px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--teal-soft);
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 24px;
}
.badge svg{width:38px;height:38px}
h1{font-size:30px;margin-bottom:12px}
.lede{color:var(--ink-soft);font-size:16px;margin-bottom:28px}
.lede strong{color:var(--ink)}
.steps{
  text-align:left;background:var(--paper);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;
  padding:22px 24px;margin-bottom:26px;
}
.steps h2{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:14px}
.steps ol{list-style:none;counter-reset:s;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:13px}
.steps li{counter-increment:s;display:flex;gap:13px;font-size:15px;color:var(--ink-soft);align-items:flex-start}
.steps li::before{
  content:counter(s);flex-shrink:0;width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--teal);color:#fff;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
}
.note{
  font-size:13.5px;color:var(--muted);background:var(--teal-soft);
  border-radius:11px;padding:13px 16px;margin-bottom:26px;line-height:1.5;
}
.note b{color:var(--teal-deep)}
.btn{
  display:inline-block;background:var(--teal);color:#fff;padding:13px 26px;border-radius:11px;
  font-weight:500;font-size:15px;text-decoration:none;transition:background .2s,transform .12s;
}
.btn:hover{background:var(--teal-deep);transform:translateY(-2px)}
.foot{margin-top:26px;font-size:13px;color:var(--muted)}
.foot a{color:var(--teal-deep);text-decoration:none}
.brand{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:30px;font-weight:600}
.brand svg{width:28px;height:28px}
@media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){*{transition:none!important}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
  <div class="brand">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M50 9 C68 36 82 52 82 64 a32 32 0 1 1 -64 0 C18 52 32 36 50 9 Z" fill="#1D9E75"/>
      <path d="M40 58 L40 50 L48 50" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      <path d="M60 74 L60 82 L52 82" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      <path d="M60 58 L60 50 L52 50" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      <path d="M40 74 L40 82 L48 82" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
    Snipdrop
  </div>

  <div class="badge">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M5 12.5l4.5 4.5L19 7.5" stroke="#1D9E75" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
  </div>

  <h1 class="display">You're now on Snipdrop Pro</h1>
  <p class="lede">Thanks for the support. Your license key is on its way to <strong>your email inbox</strong> right now.</p>

  <div class="steps">
    <h2>Activate in three steps</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Open the email from Snipdrop and copy your license key (starts with <code>sd-</code>)</li>
      <li>Click the Snipdrop icon, then go to <strong>Settings → Snipdrop Pro</strong></li>
      <li>Paste your key and click <strong>Activate</strong> — Pro unlocks instantly</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <div class="note">
    <b>Don't see the email?</b> Give it a minute and check your spam folder. Still nothing? Email
    <a href="mailto:support@niallcodes.com" style="color:var(--teal-deep)">support@niallcodes.com</a> and we'll sort it out.
  </div>

  <a class="btn" href="/snipdrop">Back to Snipdrop</a>

  <p class="foot">
    A product from <a href="https://niallcodes.com">niallcodes</a> · Florence Publishing Ltd
  </p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
